1947;;Calendar Girl;;American;;Allan Dwan;;Jane Frazee, Gail Patrick;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Calendar_Girl_(1947_film);;The film tells the story of two best friends from Boston who come to Greenwich Village in 1900, one to become a famous artist, the other to become a famous composer. The composer falls in love with the girl next door, but she is intrigued by his friend, who has secrets he feels he doesn't need to share with her.